    import Concord as ccd
import scanpy as sc
import torch

from pathlib import Path
import time
proj_name = "pbmc3k"
save_dir = Path(f"../save/{proj_name}_{time.strftime('%b%d')}/")
save_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)
file_suffix = f"{proj_name}_{time.strftime('%b%d')}"

adata = sc.datasets.pbmc3k()
adata_processed = sc.datasets.pbmc3k_processed()
adata = adata[adata_processed.obs.index]
adata.obs = adata_processed.obs
adata.obsm = adata_processed.obsm
adata.layers['counts'] = adata.X.copy()
